{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"KeyboardKitPro"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Themes","images":[{"identifier":"Page.png","type":"card"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This article describes the KeyboardKit Pro theme engine."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit has a style engine that makes it easy to customize the style of your keyboard. However, the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyleService"},{"type":"text","text":" is a bit tricky to use if you need to easily apply many different styles."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"👑 ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/KeyboardKit\/KeyboardKitPro","type":"reference"},{"text":" therefore unlocks a theme engine that can be used to easily style your keyboard with different styles, and provides you with many predefined themes, templates, and theme-based views. You can easily create custom themes as well.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Namespace","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Namespace"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit has a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme"},{"text":" type that is also a namespace for theme-related types and views, like ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/Shelf"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/ShelfItem"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Context","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Context"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit has an observable "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class that can be used to handle themes and auto-persisted "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext\/settings-swift.property","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". It also has auto-persisted "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext\/settings-swift.property","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" that can be used to persist themes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit automatically creates an instance of this class, injects it into ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardInputViewController\/state","type":"reference"},{"text":" and updates it whenever the theme changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Services","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Services"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In KeyboardKit, a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyleService\/themeBased(keyboardContext:themeContext:)","type":"reference"},{"text":" style service can be used to apply a keyboard theme:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["override func viewDidLoad() {","    super.viewDidLoad()","    setup(for: .myApp) { result in","        \/\/ Check result to see that setup was successful","        self.services.styleService = .themeBased(","            keyboardContext: state.keyboardContext,","            themeContext: state.themeContext","        )","    } ","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can inherit ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyle\/ThemeBasedStyleService"},{"text":" to customize themes even further, which lets you mix the benefits of themes and styles.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Settings","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Settings"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit has a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeSettings","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" type with theme-related state & settings. The context ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardThemeContext\/settings-swift.property","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is used by default.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Themes","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Themes"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme"},{"text":" can provide keyboard-related styles in a way that can be easily used and modified. A theme can also define style variations that can be used to customize a constrained set of theme properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit Pro unlocks a bunch of themes and style variations, as well as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyle\/ThemeBasedStyleService","isActive":true},{"text":" that lets you apply themes with the style service concept that is still used by the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardView","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit Pro unlocks many standard themes, like "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/standard","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/swifty","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/minimal","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". These themes also have style variations, that lets you vary their appearance, like the standard theme’s "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/StandardStyle\/blue","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/StandardStyle\/green","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" variations:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"title":".standard","content":[{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":3,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"standard","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"standard-blue","type":"image"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"standard-green"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]},{"title":".swifty","content":[{"numberOfColumns":3,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"swifty","type":"image"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"swifty-blue"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"swifty-green","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"row"}]},{"title":".minimal","content":[{"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type"