},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"tron-virus","type":"image"}]}]}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can get a list of all predefined themes, as well as all pre-defined style variations, using the static ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/predefined"},{"text":" properties. You can create your own themes, as well as custom style variations for all predefined themes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Views","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Views"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit Pro unlocks views in the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" namespace, that make it easy to preview and present keyboard themes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"row","columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"themeshelf"}]}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A keyboard theme ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/Shelf","type":"reference"},{"text":" can be used to list themes in a vertical list of horizontally scrolling shelves.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can use the standard ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme\/ShelfItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" to show how a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Keyboard\/Button","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" will look, or use completely custom views for the titles and items.","type":"text"}]}]}],"numberOfColumns":2}],"title":"Shelf"}]},{"type":"thematicBreak"},{"anchor":"How-to","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"How to…"},{"anchor":"create-a-custom-theme","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"…create a custom theme"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" is just a struct, you can easily create your own custom themes by just defining new static theme value types."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For instance, this theme only changes the color of the primary button:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["extension KeyboardTheme {","","    static var greenPrimary: Self {","        get throws {","            try? Self(primaryBackgroundColor: .green)","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can also use other themes as a base when creating your own custom themes, if you only want to change a small part of a theme.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For instance, this theme starts with the minimal theme and changes the color of the primary button to pink:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["extension KeyboardTheme {","","    static var pinkPrimary: Self {","        get throws {","            var theme = try? KeyboardTheme.minimal","            theme.buttonStyles[.primary]?.backgroundColor = .green","            return theme","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also create custom themes that just tweak a style variation of another theme."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For instance, this custom theme is a standard theme that applies a black tint color style variation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["extension KeyboardTheme {","